Description: Yuma Tsukumo will stop at nothing to become the Duel Masters champion, but as a rank amateur, the odds are stacked against him. Luckily, he has a mysterious spirit named Astral to help him.
Title: YU-GI-OH! ZEXAL, VOL. 2
Author: Kazuki Takahashi

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, Ichigo is still on his quest to regain his powers.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 52
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and must help usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, with his abilities returned, Ichigo confronts Ginjo.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 53
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Naruto and his allies battle an army of undead ninjas and an unexpected resurrection throws them all for a loop.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 59
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: This series is about grade-school boys who want to become professionals in the manga industry.
Title: BAKUMAN, VOL. 17
Author: Tsugumi Ohba

Description: Misao Harada can see into a magical realm where she is the bride demon of prophecy.
Title: BLACK BIRD, VOL. 15
Author: Kanoko Sakurakouji

Description: The popular apocalyptic series, which follows a group of teenagers who pilot giant robots, continues.
Title: NEON GENESIS EVANGELION, VOL. 13
Author: Yoshiyuki Sadamoto

Description: This is a story about destiny and Sakura, the princess of a moon kingdom who is fated to wield a legendary sword.
Title: SAKURA HIME: THE LEGEND OF PRINCESS SAKURA, VOL. 9
Author: Arina Tanemura

Description: Cross Academy has day and evening students, but the latter have a secret: they are vampires.
Title: VAMPIRE KNIGHT, VOL. 15
Author: Matsuri Hino

Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 8
Author: Naoko Takeuchi
